       false,
       "decimal.DecimalException.__dict__.__contains__('__await__') == False — decimal.DecimalException is the base exception class for all decimal arithmetic exceptions; it does not implement the awaitable protocol; as an Exception subclass it inherits no async protocol from Exception, BaseException, or object; verified with Python 3.12"]
